    "description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >YOU ARE THE SUPER MEGA LEGEND PHOENIX</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173980/extras/d7b12d2f1b73da3f8006a1fb932b71e5.avif?t=1752122913\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br>You’re the legendary Phoenix, the famous hero of a massive battle that happened 2,000 years ago. You took a super long nap to heal your battle wounds, but now, monsters from the land are coming to find and defeat you!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173980/extras/33ee7a3738038030158bca738da4df7b.avif?t=1752122913\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br>As a proud mythical creature, you can’t back down from a challenge, but there’s a catch—you can only use your full, super awesome power for just 11 seconds because you’re still healing.<br><br>Get ready to take down wave after wave of enemies and show them that the legend of the “Super Mega Legend Phoenix” is still alive!<br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to Play</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173980/extras/b35638ac5d6c0f7f04a5bae2e4bc9cba.poster.avif?t=1752122913\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173980/extras/b35638ac5d6c0f7f04a5bae2e4bc9cba.webm?t=1752122913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173980/extras/b35638ac5d6c0f7f04a5bae2e4bc9cba.mp4?t=1752122913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Playing is super easy!<br>But winning won’t be easy!</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173980/extras/dc460f483a424aa5a1a265948fdafbb2.poster.avif?t=1752122913\" width=600 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173980/extras/dc460f483a424aa5a1a265948fdafbb2.webm?t=1752122913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173980/extras/dc460f483a424aa5a1a265948fdafbb2.mp4?t=1752122913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>When the game starts, the keys you need to press will show up on the right side of the screen. Press the right keys to attack the monsters.<br><br>Watch out for COMBOS! Every time you press the correct key, your COMBO goes up by 1, and your attack power increases too! (+1 for each COMBO) But if you press the wrong key, your COMBO goes back to 0.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173980/extras/75fe659e9787d084fc616b31e024b9f4.poster.avif?t=1752122913\" width=560 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173980/extras/75fe659e9787d084fc616b31e024b9f4.webm?t=1752122913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173980/extras/75fe659e9787d084fc616b31e024b9f4.mp4?t=1752122913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You’ve only got 11 seconds to fight! If you don’t defeat all the enemies (LEVEL 10) in 11 seconds, you lose.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173980/extras/772e921d3c3012eced1cfc7f2fdf0bc1.poster.avif?t=1752122913\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173980/extras/772e921d3c3012eced1cfc7f2fdf0bc1.webm?t=1752122913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173980/extras/772e921d3c3012eced1cfc7f2fdf0bc1.mp4?t=1752122913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>But if you manage to take down all 10 levels of enemies in time, you win!</strong><br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >And remember, YOU ARE THE SUPER MEGA LEGEND PHOENIX</h2></strong>",
